# Load Land Cover Parameter lc = json.load(open(lc_dir)) lc_df = pd.DataFrame(lc)

lc_df["values_normalize"] = lc_df.index + 1 lc_df["palette"] = "#" + lc_df["palette"]


# Mapping from old to new values

values = lc_df["values"].to_list()

values_norm = lc_df["values_normalize"].to_list() palette = lc_df["palette"].to_list()

labels = lc_df["label"].to_list() dict_values = {}

dict_label = {} dict_palette = {}

dict_palette_hex = {}

for x in range(0, len(values)):

dict_values[values[x]] = values_norm[x] dict_label[values_norm[x]] = labels[x]

dict_palette[values_norm[x]] = ImageColor.getrgb(palette[x]) dict_palette_hex[values_norm[x]] = palette[x]


# Create colormap from values and palette cmap = ListedColormap(palette)


# Patches legend patches = [

mpatches.Patch(color=palette[i], label=labels[i]) for i in range(len(values))

]

legend = {

"handles": patches,

"bbox_to_anchor": (1.05, 1),

"loc": 2,

"borderaxespad": 0.0,

}
